# Marketing and advertising workflow

Use this rule whenever the user asks for **marketing**, **advertising**, **paid social**, **Meta / Facebook / Instagram ads**, **lead gen**, **seller acquisition**, **CPL**, **CAPI**, **marketing dashboard**, **weekly optimization packet**, **`agent_insights` marketing**, **GA4 for marketing**, or **Follow Up Boss outreach automation** tied to ads.

## Mandatory reads (in order)

1. **`docs/FACEBOOK_SELLER_GROWTH_PIPELINE.md`** — System map, layers, crons, env vars, verification commands, open follow-ups. **Canonical for architecture and data flow.**
2. **`docs/FB_SELLER_CAMPAIGN_PLAYBOOK.md`** — Launch playbook when the task is “how do we run the seller campaign.”
3. **`.cursor/skills/facebook-seller-growth/SKILL.md`** — Recurring optimization routine; append outcomes to **`docs/marketing/facebook-seller-growth-LEARNINGS.md`** after a cycle.
4. **`social_media_skills/facebook-lead-gen-ad/SKILL.md`** — When building lead-gen **creative**, form fields, or Ads Manager steps for report-style lead magnets.

## Browsable diagram export

- **`docs/FACEBOOK_SELLER_GROWTH_PIPELINE.html`** — Self-contained HTML with Mermaid diagrams. Regenerate after markdown edits: `node scripts/build-pipeline-doc-html.mjs`. Validate diagrams: `node scripts/validate-pipeline-doc-mermaid.mjs`.

## Related code (quick pointers)

| Area | Typical paths |
|------|----------------|
| Weekly marketing packet cron | `app/api/cron/marketing-optimization-report/route.ts` |
| FUB outreach cron | `app/api/cron/fub-outreach-execution/route.ts` |
